# Shared by both worker Dockerfiles and CDK image-asset staging: everything
# the in-image npm ci + tsc build regenerates stays out of the build context.
# Patterns are **-prefixed because dockerignore roots bare names, and cdk.out
# lives at packages/control/cdk.out (staging it recurses into itself).
# tsbuildinfo lives at package roots, not dist; stale buildinfo + missing dist
# makes tsc -b skip emitting, so it must be excluded alongside dist.
**/node_modules
**/.git
**/cdk.out
**/.next
**/dist
**/*.tsbuildinfo
**/.claude
**/dynamodb-local-metadata.json
